## Open-Source Tools for the Semantic Web

Basic Tools:
- RDF: Apache Jena, Redland RDF Library
- JSON-LD: JSON-LD Processor
- OWL: Protégé, OWLAPI
- SPARQL: Apache Jena Fuseki, Blazegraph
- SKOS: PoolParty (open-source core)

Advanced Tools:
- Reasoners: Pellet, HermiT
- Linked Data Platforms: Apache Marmotta, GraphDB (open-source)
- Graph Databases: Neo4j (open-source), RDF4J
- Ontology Management: WebProtégé, TopBraid Composer (Community Edition)
- Data Integration: DataHub, LODsyndesis
